{"title":"you are not allowed to push code to protected branches on this project","date":"2019-03-25T17:10:59.000Z","link":"post/322","categories":["Git"],"updated":"2019-06-23T14:42:33.077Z","content":"<p><code>you are not allowed to push code to protected branches on this project</code><br>受保护的分支。<br>解决方法：<br> <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\">新装的gitlab。GitLab一些分支默认被保护，仅仅拥有master级别的用户才能提交到保护分支，而且master分支默认是保护分支，其他用户需要通过合并issue请求来提交上去</span><br><span class=\"line\"> </span><br><span class=\"line\">Project: &quot;Settings&quot; -&gt; &quot;Repository&quot; -&gt; scroll down to &quot;Protected branches&quot;.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://github.com/1056438464/1056438464.github.io/raw/master/images/3076568899.png\" alt class=\"article-img\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"解决error: failed to push some refs to 'xxx(远程库)'","link":"post/324"},"next":{"title":"char数组转list","link":"post/320"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/322/"}